INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (1,123,'Nike Air Jordan 3  Retro',100,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/rrj0scsifzfbdjhdrmtq/air-jordan-3-retro-mens-shoe-8msLVx.jpg','The Air Jordan 3 Retro Men\'s Shoe features lightweight, visible cushioning for the comfortable fit of the original. Leather provides durability, and signature details celebrate the game-changing icon.',2000000),(7,124,'Nike Air VaporMax Flyknit 2',89,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/qdibl1vhmrkxqabgxu4n/air-vapormax-flyknit-2-mens-shoe-BPBJRb.jpg','The Nike Air VaporMax Flyknit 2 has lightweight, bouncy cushioning for a gravity-defying sensation. Flyknit fabric makes for a snug, flawless fit.',4800000),(8,125,'Nike Air Max 97 QS',200,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/tviq2pljxaro0gmc61c6/air-max-97-qs-mens-shoe-B6dsCp.jpg','The Nike Air Max 97 shook up the running world with its revolutionary full-length Nike Air unit. The Nike Air 97 QS remasters the original design with fresh colorways that are the inverse of iconic styles, the silver and gold bullet.',3700000),(9,126,'Nike Air VaporMax Plus',128,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/wjtwg6ni1swlhml25oww/air-vapormax-plus-mens-shoe-Lw8Dng.jpg','The Nike Air VaporMax Plus looks to the past to propel you into the future. This revamp nods to the super-techy Air Max Plus of 1998 with its floating cage, cushioned upper and heel logo. Revolutionary VaporMax Air technology brings it into today.',5700000),(10,127,'Nike Air Max 270',67,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/hyn4my0yzq35ol3gpdsa/air-max-270-mens-shoe-jKGdGN.jpg','The Nike Air Max 270 Men\'s Shoe is inspired by two icons of big Air: the Air Max 180 and Air Max 93. It features Nike’s biggest heel Air unit yet for a super-soft ride that feels as impossible as it looks.',8000000),(11,128,'Nike Air VaporMax Flyknit Utility',56,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/hgqsc1zx8nb3ssyfhvv3/air-vapormax-flyknit-utility-shoe-XPTbVZzp.jpg','The Nike Air VaporMax Flyknit 2 has lightweight, bouncy cushioning for a gravity-defying sensation. Flyknit fabric makes for a snug, flawless fit.',5670000),(12,129,'Nike Air VaporMax Light II',78,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/gmymnwonsiw5q65gbrdd/air-vapormax-light-ii-womens-shoe-sPdZXJ.jpg','Slip into the Nike Air VaporMax Light II Women\'s Shoe for style that\'s as tough as it is sleek. ',3600000),(13,130,'Nike Air VaporMax Utility',100,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/a7azeibx7jjguvudjl9d/air-vapormax-utility-mens-shoe-l6QV6Q.jpg','The Nike Air VaporMax Utility gets remixed to conquer dark, wet routes. A water-repellent upper helps keep your feet dry, while the toggle lacing is quick and easy to adjust. Elements throughout the upper are reflective.',4000000),(14,131,'LeBron 16',167,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/rrrygreb6eennoydmtoj/lebron-16-basketball-shoe-PjFb0x.jpg','Ball in hand and a bucket in mind, Kyrie Irving breaks down the defense using his arsenal of moves. The Kyrie 5 turbocharges his fast, all-angle attack with new cushioning technology that aligns with the curved shape of the outsole. Whether he’s breaking or banking, the Nike Air Zoom Turbo responds with a rapid return of energy.',1800000),(15,132,'PG 2.5 Pendleton',156,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/pomepujvu1z8mosbfeqa/pg-25-pendleton-shoe-lZx5Wm.jpg','Designed for one of the game\'s most versatile players, the PG 2.5 Pendleton is a refresh of Paul George\'s second signature model, with design accents courtesy of Pendleton Woolen Mills. Plush cushioning and lateral stability help you seamlessly transition from offense to defense.',2800000),(16,134,'Air Jordan 1 Mid',15,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/uctcw9h0aln0tewy45co/air-jordan-1-mid-mens-shoe-1zMCFJ.jpg','Inspired by the 1985 original, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Men\'s Shoe remembers the revolutionary shoe that took MJ through his rookie season and first All-Star game appearance. New materials and colors give it a fresh look you can wear anywhere.',179000),(17,135,'Nike React Element 55',129,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/nk01bl7nktryaovh4kkg/react-element-55-mens-shoe-KpnWKm.jpg','Borrowing design lines from heritage Nike running shoes such as the Internationalist, the Nike React Element 55 Men\'s Shoe embraces history and pushes it into the future. Nike React foam delivers lightweight comfort, while rubber outsole pods and reflective details offer a cutting-edge look that begs a reaction.',7000000),(18,136,'Nike Zoom 2K',44,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/gjwzhdivuhoqnnpv9ydw/zoom-2k-mens-shoe-KDhqfM.jpg','The legend lives on in the Nike Air Force 1 \'07, a low-cut take on the iconic AF1 that blends classic court style and striking color contrast.',6750000),(19,137,'Nike Air Trainer Huarache',90,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/jf4qo0a9liqqqnt4zlm7/air-trainer-huarache-mens-shoe-4DZccl.jpg','Named for a fish that can breathe both in the water and on land, the Nike Air Max 270 Bowfin Shoe epitomizes versatility by combining elements of trail shoes and water moccasins. It pushes this utility-inspired look into the future with the addition of Nike\'s largest Max Air unit.',3460000),(20,138,'Nike Air Max 270 SE Reflective',78,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/arwof1rr7yn0ibkz5mai/air-max-270-se-reflective-mens-shoe-6QdjFd.jpg','Boasting the first-ever Max Air unit created specifically for Nike Sportswear, the Nike Air Max 270 SE Reflective Men\'s Shoe delivers visible Air under every step. Updated for modern comfort, it nods to the original 1991 Air Max 180 with its tongue design, which features an exaggerated top and a heritage logo.',8000000),(21,139,'Nike Air Max 95 Essential',100,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/zjqgyqdam0toroxtgrac/air-max-95-essential-mens-shoe-JPe0Pd.jpg','The Nike Air Max 95 keeps the classic design lines of the 1995 original and the forefoot Max Air cushioning that made it famous.',7800000),(22,140,'Nike Zoom Pegasus Turbo',120,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/nui4yjajl7ca8cjacjxt/zoom-pegasus-turbo-mens-running-shoe-Z163c3.jpg','The Nike Zoom Pegasus Turbo is the Pegasus you know and love with major upgrades for speed. The feather-light upper looks as fast as it feels, while the revolutionary Nike ZoomX foam that was designed for elite Nike runners during the Breaking 2 attempt brings record-breaking speed and responsiveness to your daily training runs.',6900000),(23,141,'Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 35',118,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/qliunp7l0stdtemvf7an/air-zoom-pegasus-35-mens-running-shoe-kX9NZL.jpg','Made for short runs when you want a barefoot-like feel, the Nike Free RN Flyknit 2018 Men\'s Running Shoe is the lightest in the Free RN family. Its sock-like upper has more stretch yarns than previous versions, so it hugs your feet more than ever. The innovative sole has an updated construction, yet still expands and contracts with every movement. The packable design makes the shoe easy to stuff into your bag—so you can get in a few miles on the fly.',6300000),(24,142,'Nike Metcon 4',119,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/qm9t3oxze6vjhw2vro0j/metcon-4-mens-cross-training-weightlifting-shoe-rJTGV0Vy.jpg','The Metcon 4 Men\'s Cross Training/Weightlifting Shoe provides a strong, stable base, flexible support, and extreme durability for a wide range of training activities, from sprints and sled pushes to lifting and rope climbing. A new textured mesh makes it stronger, lighter, and more durable than any Metcon—ever.',4900000),(25,143,'Air Jordan 9 Retro NRG',30,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/xyhkgwedt0m2depq5ffe/air-jordan-9-retro-nrg-mens-boot-gobOZ8.jpg','Inspired by design elements from the Special Field Boot, the Air Jordan 9 NRG Men\'s Boot features a water-resistant coating and heavy tread, plus a durable leather and suede construction. Zoom Air units in the heel and forefoot provide plush, lightweight cushioning.',4500000),(26,144,'Nike Air Huarache Gripp',88,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/tsqu3arwn0xablwppuak/air-huarache-gripp-mens-shoe-XDszPr.jpg','Designed to stretch with your foot, the Nike Air Huarache has remained a sneaker staple since its 1991 debut, when it changed the face of running footwear forever. The Nike Air Huarache Gripp throws back to the original design and then ups the ante with modern details and a sure-footed tread.',5100000),(27,145,'Nike Lunar Force 1 Duckboot Low',100,'https://c.static-nike.com/a/images/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5,w_440/zdtjolbxvmqjosyhzuje/lunar-force-1-duckboot-low-mens-shoe-17wK3r.jpg','The original AF1 sneaker gets a cold-weather makeover with the Nike Lunar Force 1 \'18 Men\'s Duckboot. It\'s equipped with a water-repellent synthetic upper and a rugged outsole so you can face the elements in comfort and style.',8000000);
